### 変数

@base_url = http://localhost:5002


### サーバーの起動確認

GET {{base_url}}/ HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json


### 付喪神の一覧を取得

GET {{base_url}}/tsukumogami HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json


### 付喪神の所持状況を更新

POST {{base_url}}/tsukumogami/bakeneko HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


### 付喪神の所持状況を更新(存在しないID)

POST {{base_url}}/tsukumogami/hogehoge HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
